The **Barcodes **tab allows to configure barcodes by loading an XML file containing the information to be used by Document Composition for barcodes management.

![](data:image/jpeg;base64,)

## Inserting an XML file
- Open the desired XML file using a suitable text editor.

- Copy its text content.

- Paste the text into the barcode configuration window. During this operation, Document Composition checks that the syntax of the XML file is correct.
